# Meatvo — Cursor Rules

## 1. Project Overview

**Meatvo** is a hyperlocal raw-meat delivery platform for India. Customers browse a catalog, add items to cart, pick a delivery slot and address, pay (COD or PhonePe), and track orders in real time. Delivery riders and store admins have dedicated flows.

This is a **monorepo**:

| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `backend/` | Node.js REST API + Socket.io + PostgreSQL/Redis |
| `old_meatvo/` | Flutter customer/rider/admin mobile app |
| `admin/`, `customer/`, `delivery/` | Web SPAs served by the backend |
| `shared/` | Shared env manifest (`env-manifest.json`) |

**UX reference:** Zappfresh-inspired dark commerce UI.

---

## 2. Backend Tech Stack & Folder Structure

### Stack
- **Runtime:** Node.js (CommonJS), Express 5
- **Database:** PostgreSQL (`pg`), Redis (`ioredis`)
- **Auth:** JWT access/refresh tokens, OTP via MSG91, optional MFA (speakeasy)
- **Payments:** PhonePe gateway
- **Real-time:** Socket.io
- **Security:** Helmet, CORS, rate limiting, CSRF, CSP, RBAC, account lockout
- **Observability:** Winston, Sentry, Elasticsearch logger
- **Validation:** Joi, Zod, express-validator

### `backend/src/` structure

```
backend/src/
├── config/          # env validation, secrets (AWS SSM), security config
├── constants/       # shared constants (e.g. health)
├── db/              # postgres.js, redis.js, schema.sql, ensureSchema.js
├── middlewares/     # auth, RBAC, rate limit, error handler, validation
├── modules/         # feature modules (controller + routes + validation)
│   ├── auth/        # OTP login, JWT refresh, MFA
│   ├── users/
│   ├── addresses/
│   ├── products/
│   ├── categories/
│   ├── catalog/
│   ├── cart/        # Redis-backed cart
│   ├── orders/      # order state machine
│   ├── payments/    # PhonePe initiate/verify/webhook
│   ├── delivery/    # slots, rider orders, location
│   ├── admin/       # dashboard, CRUD, uploads
│   ├── banners/
│   ├── coupons/
│   ├── settings/    # store config, serviceability
│   ├── firebase/
│   └── uploads/
├── routes/          # health, metrics, debug
├── security/        # OTP/JWT/payment/socket security services
├── services/        # cross-module services (e.g. assignment)
├── socket/          # Socket.io init
└── utils/           # jwt, sms, response helpers, order state machine
```

Entry point: `backend/index.js` (default port **8080**).

---

## 3. Flutter Tech Stack & Folder Structure

### Stack
- **Framework:** Flutter 3.9+ (`old_meatvo/`)
- **State:** flutter_riverpod
- **HTTP:** Dio via `ApiService` / `ApiClient`
- **Navigation:** Navigator (MaterialPageRoute) + partial go_router
- **Storage:** flutter_secure_storage, shared_preferences, Hive
- **Maps:** google_maps_flutter, geolocator, geocoding
- **Real-time:** socket_io_client
- **UI:** shimmer, carousel_slider, google_fonts (Poppins)
- **Payments:** PhonePe via backend redirect URL (native SDK disabled)
- **Env:** flutter_dotenv (`.env` in assets)

### `old_meatvo/lib/` structure

```
old_meatvo/lib/
├── main.dart                 # app entry, ProviderScope, theme
├── config/                   # env_config, api_config, backend_resolver, feature_flags
├── core/
│   ├── constants/            # AppColors, AppTextStyles, AppSpacing, AppRadius (canonical)
│   └── widgets/              # meatvo_button, shimmer_loader, product_card, section_header
├── design_system/
│   ├── tokens/               # meatvo_colors, meatvo_spacing, meatvo_radii
│   └── theme/                # meatvo_theme (premium warm palette — secondary)
├── features/                 # feature-scoped providers + widgets
│   ├── catalog/
│   ├── home/
│   ├── connectivity/
│   └── tracking/
├── screens/                  # full-page UI
│   ├── auth/                 # splash, phone, OTP, login
│   ├── onboarding/           # onboarding, location setup
│   ├── home/
│   ├── cart/, checkout/
│   ├── orders/, product/, categories/, search/
│   ├── address/, profile/, settings/
│   ├── payment/
│   ├── rider/                # rider dashboard, orders, profile
│   ├── admin/                # admin dashboard, CRUD screens
│   ├── wishlist/, notifications/
│   └── ...
├── services/                 # API + domain services (ALL HTTP goes through here)
│   ├── api_client.dart       # Dio client, token refresh, interceptors
│   ├── api_service.dart      # thin wrapper over ApiClient — use this in services
│   ├── auth_service.dart, cart_service.dart, order_service.dart, ...
│   └── socket_service.dart, payment_service.dart, maps_service.dart, ...
├── providers/                # Riverpod providers (auth, cart, product, order, theme)
├── models/                   # data models
├── widgets/                  # shared UI (home, cart, checkout, location, skeletons)
├── ui/                       # design-system atoms/organisms/shells
├── theme/                    # app_theme.dart (legacy light/dark)
└── utils/                    # app_colors.dart (DEPRECATED — use AppColors)
```

